headline: Looking at the Changing Narrative for Unite Group After Index Shift and Analyst Target Moves
summary: Unite Group’s consensus analyst price target has seen a modest decrease, moving from £9.68 to £9.40, following the latest review of the company’s outlook. This slight adjustment comes as analysts weigh continued optimism around international student demand and sector positioning, while also considering emerging uncertainties in the broader market.
